<template><h1 id="自动连接" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#自动连接" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax#autolink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">自动连接<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h1>
<p>Markdown支持为URL和电子邮件地址创建&quot;自动&quot;链接的快捷方式：只需将URL或电子邮件地址用尖括号<code>&lt;&gt;</code>括起来。这意味着，如果您想显示URL或电子邮件地址的实际文本，并使其成为可点击的链接，您可以这样作：</p>
<p>可点击链接Markdown语法代码：<code>&lt;超链接地址&gt;</code></p>
<div class="language-markdown ext-md line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-markdown"><code>&lt;https://ilyl.life/zh/life/literature/markdown/>

<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>markwodn@example.com</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br></div></div><p><a href="https://ilyl.life/zh/life/literature/markdown/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://ilyl.life/zh/life/literature/markdown/<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
